=== affine_injective (per-position + pinning) ===
2*oh+wh (wh range 2) injective: true
K*i+k (k range <= K) injective: true
3*i+j (j range <= 3) injective: true
triangular (s1, s1+s2) injective: true
i+j (both ranges > 1) injective: false
stride*o+k (k range > stride) injective: false
3*a+4*b over (3,2) injective (known-incomplete): false
=== is_injective (with product-iterator coverage) ===
is_injective 2*oh+wh: true
is_injective i+j: false
is_injective with uncovered contraction symbol: false
